title: ‘These Guys Are Nasty’: Houston Thrives With Unexpected Stars
description: Cristian Javier and Framber Valdez were never top prospects, but Houston’s Dominican starters are part of a superb group of Astros pitchers starring in the World Series.
dc:creator: Tyler Kepner
media:description: Cristian Javier was 11-9 with a 2.54 E.R.A. during the regular season. He has won consecutive postseason starts, the second of which was part of a combined no-hitter.
